Name: hfda
Version: 0.1.1
Summary: Implementation of Higuchi Fractal Dimension Analysis.
Home-page: https://github.com/hiroki-kojima/HFDA
Author: Hiroki Kojima
Author-email: 7316072@gmail.com
License: BSD
Description: HFDA
        ====
        
        Implementation of Higuchi Fractal Dimension Analysis.
        
        Install
        ----------
        
        .. code-block:: text
        
            pip install hfda
        
        Example
        -------
        
        .. code-block:: python
        
            import numpy as np
            import hfda
        
        
            N = np.power(2, 15)
            X = np.sin(np.linspace(0, 1000, N))
            k_max = 5
        
            D = hfda.measure(X, k_max)
        
Platform: UNKNOWN
